1:  Download netCDF version >= 4.0 
      http://www.unidata.ucar.edu/software/netcdf

2:  Compile (usually "./configure;./make install;make test")
2b: If needed: "./configure --prefix=/home/yourUser/local/netcdf"

3:  Download ScientificPython >= 2.8
      http://sourcesup.cru.fr/projects/scientific-py
    NOTE: This is NOT SciPy !!!

4:  If needed: edit setup.py: set netcdf_prefix to same as above

5:  python setup.py install 
    (remember --prefix=/home/yourUser/local/python-packages)
